missionEventData.data1: It's time for us to strike back. The Imperial forces led by the Star Destroyer Invincible, depleted of supplies from their attacks on Briggia, are awaiting resupply from a Freighter Convoy. Your strike team will consist of two X-Wings and two Y-Wings. Keep the Tie Fighters away from the Y-Wings and watch out for reinforcements. As soon as the Freighters have been destroyed, hyperspace out.

missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: Red Squadron head to the jump point immediately. Blue Squadron is already en route.
This is Red Leader, we'll take out the Ties. Blue Squadron, focus on the Ranger.
This is Red Leader, we're joining the attack on the Ranger.
Okay, now it's time to finish the job. Take out that convoy!
The Invincible is jumping in. Time to make our exit.
All Rebel craft cease your flight and prepare for boarding!

missionEventData.data3: Well done, while the loss of their convoy wont stop the offensive, it will slow down their operation forcing them to use more of their ships for convoy duty, decreasing their impact on the front line
